Package gov.nih.nlm.meme.exception

Provides all classes for shared MEME exceptions.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
ErrorCatalog This class maps mnemonics to error messages.
Version The Version class provides package version information for gov.nih.nlm.meme.exception package.
 

Exception Summary
ActionException Generically represents an exception caused by a failure of the ActionEngine to process an action.
AdministratorException Generically represents an exception that was caused by an administrator mistake.
ApplicationException Generically represents an exception that was caused by a user interaction.
AtomicActionException Generically represents an exception caused by an attempt to execute an atomic action.
BadValueException Generically represents an exception caused by a variable in some class that has an invalid or badly formatted value.
ClientException Generically represents an exception that was caused by a client request.
ConcurrencyException Generically represents an exception that was caused by two or more things happening at the same time.
DataSourceConnectionException Generically represents an exception caused by an attempt to connect to a MEMEDataSource.
DataSourceException Generically represents an exception caused by the use of a MEMEDataSource.
DeveloperException Generically represents an exception that was caused by a developer mistake.
ExecException Generically represents an exception caused by the attempt to execute a command.
ExpiredSessionException Generically represents an exception caused by an attempt to access an expried session.
ExternalResourceException Generically represents an exception that was caused by a failure external to the system.
FailedToConnectException Represents an inability to connecdt to the server.
HTTPResponseException Generically represents an exception caused by a HTTP response with a status code other than 200.
InitializationException Generically represents an exception that was caused by initialization process.
IntegrityViolationException Generically represents an exception caused by a failure while checking integrity constraints.
LvgServerException Generically represents an exception caused by the attempt to normalize a string via the MIDServices.
MailException Generically represents an exception caused by a failed attempt to send email.
MEMEException This is a wrapper around Exception which is the base class for the MEME exception architecture.
MidsvcsException Generically represents an exception caused by the attempt to use the MIDServices.
MissingDataException Generically represents an exception caused by missing data in the database.
MissingPropertyException Generically represents an exception caused by missing property.
PoolOverflowException Generically represents an exception caused by a pool overflow.
ProtocolException Generically represents an exception caused by an error in handling of a network protocol.
ProtocolParseException Generically represents an exception caused by a badly formatted network protocol request.
ReflectionException Generically represents an exception caused by the use of the Java reflection API.
StaleDataException Generically represents an exception that was caused an editing client attempting to change core data based on stale in-memory objects.
UnknownStateException Represents an inability to connecdt to the server.
UserInputException Generically represents an exception caused during a user interaction.
XMLParseException Generically represents an exception caused while attempting to parse an XML document.
